songs.title: Imagine
songs.description: Imagine is a song by John Lennon that promotes peace and harmony.

songs.title: Happy
songs.description: Happy is a song by Pharrell Williams that celebrates happiness and joy.

songs.title: Let It Go
songs.description: Let It Go is a song from the movie Frozen that encourages letting go of fears and embracing one's true self.

songs.title: Bohemian Rhapsody
songs.description: Bohemian Rhapsody is a song by Queen that features various styles and genres in a complex and epic composition.

songs.title: I Will Survive
songs.description: I Will Survive is a song by Gloria Gaynor that expresses resilience and empowerment after a breakup.
